def _unstack_multiple(data, clocs, fill_value=None):
    if len(clocs) == 0:
        return data

    index = data.index

    if isinstance(data, Series):
        unstacked = data.unstack(clocs, fill_value=fill_value)
    else:
        unstacked = data.unstack(clocs, fill_value=fill_value)

        if isinstance(unstacked.index, MultiIndex):
            levels = [unstacked.index.levels[0]] + [index.levels[i] for i in range(index.nlevels) if i not in clocs]
            codes = [unstacked.index.codes[0]] + [index.codes[i] for i in range(index.nlevels) if i not in clocs]
            names = [None] + [index.names[i] for i in range(index.nlevels) if i not in clocs]
            comp_ids, obs_ids = compress_group_index(get_compressed_ids(codes[0]), sort=False)
            recons_codes = decons_obs_group_ids(comp_ids, obs_ids, [len(x) for x in levels], codes, xnull=False)

            new_columns = MultiIndex(levels=levels, codes=recons_codes, names=names, verify_integrity=False)
            unstacked.columns = new_columns

    return unstacked
